Invocation Name: chelsea football club songs
des:
Chelsea Football Club Songs will bring the song of Stamford Bridge right to you. Sing along to the famous popular chants and get fired up for game day. This skill will warm the hearts of any blues fan and teach your friends and family the lyric of the club. Let's go blues!

Is it game day? Ask Alexa to open Chelsea Football Club Songs and then say, "It's game day!" You will appreciate her response.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
